{"tid":2030041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有上開連登既台灣朋友們：中共五年內必派兵武統台灣","createTime":"2020-05-22T14:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T15:13:22.000Z","uid":113435,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c5fc4c3d34ed5d941341fb0eca9f67397a87b1","tid":2030041,"uid":113435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:01:38.000Z","msg":"中共為咗維穩，做得出直接廢除香港既「一國兩制」。下一步，絕對有機會派兵攻下台灣。<br />\n<br />\n美國，到時會唔會出兵就唔一定，就算簽咗協防協議，都唔一定會派兵，可能最多又係制裁或者打口水戰。<br />\n<br />\n希望台灣人呢幾年養精蓄銳，加強軍事訓練，準備打呢場硬仗。"},{"pid":"61326ec671385603908b3d132b26f0d87b772f34","tid":2030041,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:02:42.000Z","msg":"台灣國軍請準備"},{"pid":"3038575fcaadd46165a740587abee39f84c9384f","tid":2030041,"uid":262035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"請大家將524 行動正名為反國安法大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2029954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2029954</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fbf53a88b883da1675a2e97dba2f2589cd3628cc","tid":2030041,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:16:31.000Z","msg":"台灣就真係有美帝射住啦<br />\n<br />\n怕春咩"},{"pid":"4deb6cd2219fdb980e0037f9b1c682a0550d42ba","tid":2030041,"uid":154486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:18:24.000Z","msg":"不過台灣可能會外圍島嶼被支共侵佔<br />\n以供牆內人擼炮之用"},{"pid":"a4f3ec7aaf5bc69773b623d112e367a476d35fda","tid":2030041,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbf53a88b883da1675a2e97dba2f2589cd3628cc","tid":2030041,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:16:31.000Z","msg":"台灣就真係有美帝射住啦<br />\n<br />\n怕春咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:23:27.000Z","msg":"難講啦<br />\n一陣反手賣咗台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e433541e67483d85bd37def5c4ee0edaa5297a","tid":2030041,"uid":25573,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:26:32.000Z","msg":"如果美國對香港都係得把口<br />\n台灣都自身難保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034273811d227ca770797c7b25ee5447390435ad","tid":2030041,"uid":72304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"有時真係覺得連登仔on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你估支那咩, 簽左野又唔算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一島鍊呀醒小小啦好冇呀, 最近先話要用高雄港"},{"pid":"b07da11a106f18295b8dcdf1e9bae4a7abeaf825","tid":2030041,"uid":39010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"80e433541e67483d85bd37def5c4ee0edaa5297a","tid":2030041,"uid":25573,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:26:32.000Z","msg":"如果美國對香港都係得把口<br />\n台灣都自身難保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:29:01.000Z","msg":"今次對香港的回應 其實有一部份影響到台灣的信心"},{"pid":"ba38756a20a377e52ac12e26f78b724874013755","tid":2030041,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:29:24.000Z","msg":"又美國唔會幫台灣論，吹左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比你中共算準美國唔會幫台灣既，唔一早出撚左兵咩駛口交幾十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bafad54fa8d9ba31528ff09b071b4739c4cf314","tid":2030041,"uid":258374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"183ac37219f5d9d215cbf539a7ae8811baebcc92","tid":2030041,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b07da11a106f1